parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Forward Collision Warning and Automatic Emergency Braking System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the forward collision warning and automatic emergency braking system can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities, as the vehicle does not alert the driver or take evasive action to prevent or mitigate a collision.
symptoms: The vehicle does not alert the driver of a potential frontal collision
the vehicle does not begin braking automatically
